    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用 RPG MAKER MZ 制作，请注意以下特点。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标仅在初始菜单和战斗中可用。在游戏模式下，仅可使用键盘，以提供更好的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >启动全屏模式，请按 &quot;F4&quot;。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/3552af067b2fe58fa68beb35be750447.avif?t=1769538812\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>赫弗利特少女的过去即将揭晓！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是一个故事，而是一面映照灵魂的镜子。每一步都将带你沉浸在赫弗利特少女 <strong>Sutelz Selz</strong> 的情感之中——温暖人心的喜悦，以及刻骨铭心的痛苦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验失去、思念与希望的交错，在旅途中建立深刻的羁绊，让这段旅程的回响远远超越游戏本身。即使故事结束，它的情感仍将伴随你前行。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激烈战斗，简单而富有策略性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/81190365e936e9327a67d9a81a52c0c3.poster.avif?t=1769538812\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/81190365e936e9327a67d9a81a52c0c3.webm?t=1769538812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/81190365e936e9327a67d9a81a52c0c3.mp4?t=1769538812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✔<strong>战斗语音</strong>🎙</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/4a7da8acc0a3008b903539928af2de0a.poster.avif?t=1769538812\" width=432 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/4a7da8acc0a3008b903539928af2de0a.webm?t=1769538812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/4a7da8acc0a3008b903539928af2de0a.mp4?t=1769538812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚠ <strong>注意：本游戏包含脏话</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/a546a1b9008709a903fd1499e60cb1d4.avif?t=1769538812\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶ 7 个任务，2 位可操作角色（Henry &amp; Orion）<br>▶ 深邃剧情，隐喻世界、人生与心理健康<br>▶ 独特叙事风格，结合 2D 画面与经典配乐<br>▶ 主要与次要角色皆具有鲜明个性，令人印象深刻<br>▶ 充满趣味的玩法，包括游乐园、农场区域，以及完全自由的购物选择，直接影响游戏体验<br>▶ <strong>战斗模式、战前对话及特定剧情均配有角色语音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012810/extras/a5cf599063bb51ec038cab47c792f9f7.avif?t=1769538812\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个不同于地球的星球上，人类与赫弗利特人共同生存。<br>与人类不同，赫弗利特人的寿命仅有 <strong>20 年</strong>，然而，赫弗利特少女仍在日复一日的心理与情感压力中挣扎……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sutelz Selz</strong>，幼年时被掳走，如今必须服从某个男人的命令……作为交换，他将给予她第二次生存的机会……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存，人与赫弗利特人匆忙建立友谊……<br>在生死未卜的战斗中挣扎，每一天都不确定是否能活着回家……<br>对自由的渴望、对愿望的执着……<br>她将经历这一切……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Falling Ever - Lost in Time》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场旅程中，见证女主角 <strong>17 至 19 岁</strong> 的人生篇章。<br>直面内心挑战，探索精美绘制的场景，投身策略战斗，体验一场关于 <strong>友情与牺牲</strong> 的深刻叙事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，当一切崩塌，她唯一的选择便是孤独，以此面对那些无法磨灭的伤痕……<br>在被迫度过的偷盗生涯里，她的命运又将如何？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Falling Ever - Lost in Time》</strong> 邀请你一同踏上这场难以忘怀的旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆制作团队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＜剧本 / 游戏设计 / 场景＞</strong><br>Lucas Vacari Gomes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＜美术＞</strong><br>Krato Naka, Lucas Vacari Gomes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＜LOGO 设计＞</strong><br>Harsha</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＜作曲 / 作词＞</strong><br>Lucas Vacari Gomes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>＜配音＞</strong><br>Sutelz Selz - Ishizaki Miho</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆插件与作者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LL_GalgePauseSign - ルルの教会<br>LJJ_skipPartCommand - Accendor<br>Ritter_TittleMovie - Ritter<br>Ritter_Loading Screen - Ritter<br>Multi-Layer HP Gauge - VisuStella<br>WeakenessPopups - VisuStella<br>VisuMZ_0_CoreEngine - VisuStella<br>VisuMZ_1_BattleCore - VisuStella<br>VisuMZ_3_VisualCutinEffect - VisuStella<br>TorigoyaMZ_FrameTween - Rutan(ru_shalm)<br>TorigoyaMZ_SkillCutIn - Rutan(ru_shalm)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆素材</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>素材 1:</strong> 游乐园场景 Tile set<br>(C) WataruNakanami</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>素材 2:</strong> TIME FANTASY: ANIMALS<br>(C) finalbossblues</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>素材 3:</strong> Future Fantasy<br>(C) finalbossblues</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆翻译</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英语:</strong><br>Douglas Almeida - @designdouglas</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日语:</strong><br>Lucas Vacari Gomes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆音效合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pond5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock músicas provided by AltrusianGraceMedia, from Pond5;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock músicas provided by Sounder_Music, from Pond5;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stock músicas provided by RobertSlump, from Pond5.</p>",
